```lisp
(:action insert
    :parameters (?item - object ?structure1 - structure ?structure2 - structure)
    :precondition (and
                    (found ?item)
                    (has_split ?structure1)
                    (not (inserted ?item ?structure1))
                  )
    :effect (and
             (inserted ?item ?structure1)
             (horizontal_frame_formed ?item ?structure1 ?structure2)))

(:action dig
    :parameters (?entity - agent ?task - task)
    :precondition (and (not (task_completed ?entity ?task)))
    :effect (task_completed ?entity ?task))

(:action find
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?target - entity)
    :precondition (and
                    (not (found ?target))
                    (suitable ?target)
                   )
    :effect (found ?target))

(:action search
  :parameters (?agent - agent ?target - entity ?location - place)
  :precondition (and
                  (at ?agent ?location)
                  (not (found ?agent ?target))
                  (search_conditions ?target ?location)
                )
  :effect (found ?agent ?target))

(:action pick
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?source - entity ?item - object)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?agent ?source)
      (identifiable ?source)
      (available ?source ?item)
      (desirable ?item ?agent)
    )
    :effect (and
      (picked ?agent ?item)
      (not (available ?source ?item))))

(:action collect
  :parameters (?agent - agent ?resource - object)
  :precondition (and (available ?resource) (not (collected ?resource)))
  :effect (collected ?resource))
```
